{"tid":1789382,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"今日經過優品360比防暴禁低逼我買野，我屌！","createTime":"2019-12-19T10:23:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-21T15:01:21.000Z","uid":184099,"like":16,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0778b00ebcc2f756a5e0e377696df9a7506d6362","tid":1789382,"uid":184099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T10:23:24.000Z","msg":"有少少長，耐心睇。<br />\n<br />\n我=<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n防暴=<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日我著住黑衫，真係普通黑衣服。<br />\n無帶口罩，24歲。<br />\n起銅鑼灣，經過優品360既時候。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n突然！<br />\n有兩個防暴無啦啦一下衝埋黎禁我落地下。<br />\n我屌？！？？？？？？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：咩事阿死黑...sorry ，啊sir咩事？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">買野！做咩經過藍店唔買野？你係味搞黃色經濟圈？你係味港獨？你係味黑社會？你係味搞文革？</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：屌？我唔買藍店就係黑社會？唔買藍店就係文革？你無野啊？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">你係味唔買啊？唔買=罷買=搞黃色經濟圈！</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：點解要針對我啊！其他人經過你唔搞？搞我？香港仲有法治既？2047都味到就咁！屌你老母臭係！<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">無帶銀包啊屌！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我起死都唔買既情況下，比防暴拉左翻狗屋，被控「煽動國家顛覆政權罪」同「侮辱公職人員罪」，保釋左出黎。下個月提堂。隨時坐10幾碌。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我到而加都諗唔明，到底我犯左咩法。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解無帶銀包，唔買藍店就無啦啦要我坐10幾碌？<br />\n仲要無律師夠膽幫我維權。<br />\n今次坐撚硬。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔記得講，而加係2023年。"},{"pid":"44f9ee0a1a3ade521291ff92a18265794143da22","tid":1789382,"uid":184099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T10:24:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c33cd54a00330b4f2f04f3eb825dcc11e3418d43","tid":1789382,"uid":293539,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T10:41:37.000Z","msg":"咪撚on9啦咁大個人"},{"pid":"fb412df188a8964b47ffc484b1d524ef6d7dc154","tid":1789382,"uid":73464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T14:46:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vQKs1qe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvQKs1qe.jpg&h=4ddc159c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8caabf300d6c818b06b098986735550d2345ff7c","tid":1789382,"uid":194325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T15:01:21.000Z","msg":"大家星期六有時間，記住加入香港金融業職工總會做會員呀！<br />\n<br />\n我哋可唔可以為大家發聲，可以做到咩地步，全靠會員的支持<br />\n<br />\n冇會員，政府點解要理你呢，資方點解要理你呢...<br />\n<br />\n所以唔好等，今日就加入啦<br />\n<br />\nPS: 就算唔係金融界的同業，都麻煩like and share，俾多一個人睇到，就多一分機會團結同路人，拜托拜托🙏<br />\n<br />\n#香港金融業職工總會<br />\n#香港金總<br />\n#HKFU<br />\n#收會員<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/107457800635080/posts/159723118741881/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F107457800635080%2Fposts%2F159723118741881%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=d86Hk5Pgd4X%2FjIl3nTqvfGg5BW3O7pEdz%2F%2BecHjXtrw%3D&h=a3b4b991\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/107457800635080/posts/159723118741881/?d=n</a>"}]}